OL,3,CHospital fire started by solar panels
OL,5,FA fire which destroyed part of a
OL,6,Fhospital in North Yorkshire is thought
OL,7,Fto have been started by solar panels
OL,8,Fon the building's roof.
OL,10,FPatients and staff had to be moved
OL,11,Fwhen the blaze at Malton and Norton
OL,12,FDistrict Hospital on 8 July gutted the
OL,13,FSpringwood unit, which provides mental
OL,14,Fhealth services.
OL,16,FIn a statement, Tees Esk and Wear
OL,17,FValleys NHS Trust, said an
OL,18,Finvestigation was continuing.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
