OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1784900896
OL,3,CHospital fire started by solar panels
OL,5,FIt added: "However, North Yorkshire
OL,6,FFire and Rescue Service has
OL,7,Festablished that the fire most likely
OL,8,Fstarted at one of the solar panels on
OL,9,Fthe roof of the building.
OL,11,F"Due to the damage sustained to the
OL,12,Fsolar panels during the fire, it has
OL,13,Fnot been possible to determine any
OL,14,Ffurther details."
OL,16,FA trust spokesperson thanked emergency
OL,17,Fservices for their swift response.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
