OL,3,CHospital fire started by solar panels
OL,5,FThey added: "The safety of our staff
OL,6,Fand the people we care for remains our
OL,7,Fpriority. We have robust fire safety
OL,8,Fmeasures in place across our trust,
OL,9,Fincluding regular fire alarm testing
OL,10,Fand fire safety checks."
